// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0743 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e8691b6a-20b5-51ef-99cf-80cc44322d8d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
